{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make learning the countries of the world in school part of the curriculum",
        "additional_details": "I love Geography myself, learning countries, their flags and things about them and I think this is very useful in the modern era to help children understand other cultures, races, beliefs and living styles.",
        "background": "It is important for children to learn about the wider world. I believe learning the 197 countries of the world and things about them in Geography lessons can help children understand other cultures, something which is important in such a diverse world we live in.",
